To build and run Flash, please follow the procedures below:

[Build Flash]

copy ~/flash-example/sites/soprano.mcs.anl.gov to ~/flash-example/sites/<your machine hostname>.mcs.anl.gov
change the location of the itl and diy libs in line 119 of ~/flash-example/sites/<hostname>/Makefile.h to their location on your machine. Here itl means the ITL wrapper.
cd ~/flash-example
./setup_lssread.cmd_UG_64
cd object
make

[Run Flash]
cd ~/flash-example/run/vn_128_2
mpiexec -n 8 ../../object/flash3

Teng-Yok Lee
